966
00:37:28,199 --> 00:37:28,719
Wow, so tacky.

967
00:37:37,119 --> 00:37:38,199
Is it really that bad?

968
00:37:39,239 --> 00:37:39,800
Bad.

969
00:37:40,039 --> 00:37:40,719
Very bad.

970
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:42,960
A man

971
00:37:43,199 --> 00:37:44,119
