972
00:37:44,639 --> 00:37:45,360
Learn from your dad.

973
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:47,760
Take her to luxury stores

974
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:48,480
and shop around.

975
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:49,960
Then a fancy restaurant

976
00:37:50,239 --> 00:37:50,920
for dinner.

977
00:37:51,239 --> 00:37:52,920
Then find a nice bar

978
00:37:53,159 --> 00:37:53,880
and get a little tipsy.

979
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,280
And flowers.

980
00:37:57,079 --> 00:37:58,480
Fill the whole room with them.

981
00:37:58,639 --> 00:37:59,840
Stop making things up,

982
00:37:59,840 --> 00:38:00,320
