992
00:38:15,239 --> 00:38:15,960
After I ate it,

993
00:38:15,960 --> 00:38:17,400
my whole stomach felt warm.

994
00:38:17,559 --> 00:38:18,960
I was moved to tears.

995
00:38:19,199 --> 00:38:20,320
Cried my makeup off.

996
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:21,719
You drank too much yesterday, right?

997
00:38:23,679 --> 00:38:24,960
Do you know romance at all?

998
00:38:25,400 --> 00:38:25,920
Bye.

999
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:33,000
Just a bowl of noodles.

1000
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:35,920
Can it really work?

1001
00:38:39,880 --> 00:38:41,719
1,761 days.

1002
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:45,639
Eating, sleeping,

1003
00:38:46,199 --> 00:38:47,360
working, and studying.

1004
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:50,519
Those four things,

1005
00:38:51,800 --> 00:38:53,239
I did them all half-alive.

1006
00:38:56,239 --> 00:38:58,320
Every day, I stared at the bars

1007
00:38:59,760 --> 00:39:01,360
and thought about every step

1008
00:39:03,239 --> 00:39:04,239
I would take after getting out.

1009
00:39:05,639 --> 00:39:06,639
Nuo hates me

1010
00:39:07,320 --> 00:39:08,239
because she doesn't know

1011
00:39:08,239 --> 00:39:09,519
how cruel this world is.

1012
00:39:10,719 --> 00:39:11,760
But I do.

1013
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:12,920
I was hard on her

1014
00:39:13,079 --> 00:39:14,039
so she would understand

1015
00:39:14,079 --> 00:39:15,239
