1031
00:39:51,320 --> 00:39:52,400
No matter how much she hates me,

1032
00:39:54,320 --> 00:39:56,000
I have to give her a better life.

1033
00:39:58,079 --> 00:39:59,639
She is my daughter.

1034
00:40:01,079 --> 00:40:02,400
No one gets to bully her.

1035
00:40:06,159 --> 00:40:06,960
I know

1036
00:40:08,679 --> 00:40:09,840
Chen Liyang

1037
